title: Regarding redeployment of Dego NFT Smart Contract on BSC
body:
Dear DEGO community members:

I hope you are well. 
Due to the abuse of bots in recent campaign of Claiming Picks, few participants front ran and claimed 3800 + Picks including 4 Kryptonite Picks and disturbed the fairness of this event.  

So we have paused the Claim and NFT Market for the time being, pending for a perfect solution. 
Hence, we would like to propose the following: 

1.Scrap the previous DEGO NFT contract on BSC and switch to a new one.
2.The team will perform a new airdrop and introduce a whitelist mechanism. 
3.We estimated this redeployment of contract and airdrop will cost 1,000 BNB, which will be borne by the team. 
4.The following groups of participants who have contributed to DEGO project will be prioritised for the whitelist, 

1.Holders of DEGO LP tokens on Uniswap 
2.Traders who traded DEGO on Uniswap 
3.Dear supporters who donated 
4.Promoters
5.Participants in a new and fairer campaign

KR
Core team
Dego.finance
